<Layout title="The Action Gap | PresciaIQ Insights — Foundation Series Issue 04" description="Why most predictive AI deployments fail, and the four conditions that fix them. The model works. The organisation does not. Here is how to change that.">
  <article class="pt-28 pb-20 px-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <a href="/insights" class="text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground mb-8 inline-block">← Back to Insights</a>
